Velometer Bicycle Counter


=== Notices ===
* Bicycle counter value gets saved every 5 minutes
  NOTE: counts between power cycle and last save will be lost

* RTC will reset bicycle counter to 0 at the start of every day (midnight)


=== Sourced examples ===

Pressure sensor smoothing (running average)
http://arduino.cc/en/Tutorial/Smoothing

EEPROM
http://playground.arduino.cc/Code/EEPROMWriteAnything

DS1337 RTC
http://arduino.cc/forum/index.php?topic=38077.0
